      "description": "We are excited to offer this wonderful vehicle that has been well-maintained and remains in good, reliable condition! It drives smoothly and has a very clean interior and exterior, showing only the minor signs of regular use you'd expect from a cared-for car. This is a fantastic opportunity to own a solid, dependable vehicle that is ready for many more miles on the road!",
