    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready to own a masterpiece! This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking every bit as pristine as the day it was first sold. It has been meticulously maintained, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that still feels brand new. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is the one for you!",
