    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is clean overall, though it does show some light surface scratches and a few minor chips on the hood from normal highway driving. Inside, the cabin is tidy with minimal wear on the upholstery and all electronic features functioning as they should. It's a reliable choice for anyone looking for a solid, ready-to-drive vehicle with plenty of life left.",
