    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and performing as if it just left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior is pristine, showing zero signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a silent engine and seamless shifting, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly like-new condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
